title: Consider the Population
text: Think about the percentage of people who might face challenges in accessing certain services.

title: Common Statistics
text: Remember that a significant portion of the population often experiences accessibility issues.

title: Look at the Options
text: Consider which option seems most reasonable based on common knowledge about accessibility.

title: Eliminate the Extremes
text: Remove the options that seem too low or too high to be realistic.

title: Focus on the Middle
text: Concentrate on the options that are neither too low nor too high.
